OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777061157
OL,3,CUS soldier involved in Maduro capture
OL,4,C'won $400,000 by insider betting'
OL,6,FA soldier involved in the US operation
OL,7,Fto capture Venezuelan President
OL,8,FNicolas Maduro has been charged with
OL,9,Fusing classified information about the
OL,10,Fmission to win more than $400,000
OL,11,F(about #296,400) betting online.
OL,13,FGannon Ken Van Dyke, 38, was involved
OL,14,Fin the planning and execution of
OL,15,Fcapturing Maduro for about a month
OL,16,Fbefore it happened on January 3,
OL,17,Faccording to the federal prosecutor's
OL,18,Foffice.
OL,26,@pD@Frp
