PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777061157
OL,3,CUS soldier involved in Maduro capture
OL,4,C'won $400,000 by insider betting'
OL,6,FHe is accused of using sensitive
OL,7,Finformation relating to the operation
OL,8,Fto make a series of bets on prediction
OL,9,Fmarket site Polymarket relating to
OL,10,FMaduro leaving power by January 31.
OL,12,FVan Dyke had signed nondisclosure
OL,13,Fagreements promising to not divulge
OL,14,F"any classified or sensitive
OL,15,Finformation" related to the
OL,16,Foperations, prosecutors said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
