PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777061157
OL,3,CUS soldier involved in Maduro capture
OL,4,C'won $400,000 by insider betting'
OL,6,FHe has been charged by the Justice
OL,7,FDepartment with unlawful use of
OL,8,Fconfidential government information
OL,9,Ffor personal gain, theft of nonpublic
OL,10,Fgovernment information, commodities
OL,11,Ffraud, wire fraud and making an
OL,12,Funlawful monetary transaction.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FThe charges mean he could face years
OL,20,Fin prison.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
