PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777061157
OL,3,CUS soldier involved in Maduro capture
OL,4,C'won $400,000 by insider betting'
OL,6,FFBI Director Kash Patel said Van Dyke
OL,7,Fhad allegedly taken advantage of his
OL,8,Fposition "to profit off of a righteous
OL,9,Fmilitary operation".
OL,11,FThe Commodity Futures Trading
OL,12,FCommission - the federal agency that
OL,13,Fregulates prediction markets - has
OL,14,Falso filed a parallel complaint
OL,15,Fagainst Van Dyke.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
