PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777061157
OL,3,CUS soldier involved in Maduro capture
OL,4,C'won $400,000 by insider betting'
OL,6,FIt alleges that he moved $35,000
OL,7,F(#26,000) from his personal bank
OL,8,Faccount into a cryptocurrency exchange
OL,9,Faccount on December 26, a little over
OL,10,Fa week before US forces would fly into
OL,11,FCaracas and seize Maduro.
OL,13,FVan Dyke is then accused of using more
OL,14,Fthan $32,500 (#24,000) to make a
OL,15,Fseries of bets between December 30 and
OL,16,FJanuary 2, just hour before the first
OL,17,Fmissiles would fall on
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777061157
OL,3,CUS soldier involved in Maduro capture
OL,4,C'won $400,000 by insider betting'
OL,6,FHe allegedly placed those bets between
OL,7,FDecember 30 and January 2, with the
OL,8,Fvast majority occurring just hours
OL,9,Fbefore the first missiles would fall
OL,10,Fon the Venezuelan capital.
OL,12,FThe bets on Maduro leaving power
OL,13,Fresulted in more than $404,000
OL,14,F(#299,400) of profits, the complaint
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FBets on three other Venezuela-related
OL,18,Fcontracts netted the solider more than
OL,19,F$5,000 (#3,700), according to the
OL,20,Fdocument.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
