FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777061157
OL,3,CUS soldier involved in Maduro capture
OL,4,C'won $400,000 by insider betting'
OL,6,F"The defendant was entrusted with
OL,7,Fconfidential information about US
OL,8,Foperations and yet took action that
OL,9,Fendangered US national security and
OL,10,Fput the lives of American service
OL,11,Fmembers in harm's way," said Michael
OL,12,FSelig, the commission's chairman.
OL,14,FVan Dyke allegedly put most of the
OL,15,Fmoney he won in a foreign
OL,16,Fcryptocurrency vault and then into a
OL,17,Fnew brokerage account, and then asked
OL,18,FPolymarket to delete his account,
OL,19,Fclaiming he'd lost access to his
OL,20,Femail, the federal prosecutor's office
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
