PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777061157
OL,3,CUS soldier involved in Maduro capture
OL,4,C'won $400,000 by insider betting'
OL,6,FUS lawmakers are considering
OL,7,Flegislation to ban prediction markets
OL,8,Ffrom allowing bets on war,
OL,9,Fassassinations or terrorist attacks,
OL,10,Fafter several new Polymarket accounts
OL,11,Fwon money on whether a ceasefire deal
OL,12,Fwould occur between the US and Iran.
OL,14,FOn Wednesday, online betting market
OL,15,FKalshi fined and suspended three
OL,16,Fcongressional candidates who allegedly
OL,17,Fwagered on the outcome of their own
OL,18,Felections.
OL,20,FThis is not the first time Polymarket
OL,21,Fhas faced controversy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
