OL,3,CUS soldier involved in Maduro capture
OL,4,C'won $400,000 by insider betting'
OL,6,FFrench police are investigating
OL,7,Fwhether national weather forecasting
OL,8,Fequipment was tampered with after
OL,9,Fmultiple successful bets were made on
OL,10,Fa series of unusual temperature
OL,11,Freadings in April.
OL,13,FOne account made $14,000 (about
OL,14,F#10,300) for correctly predicting
OL,15,Ftemperatures would jump to 22C on the
OL,16,Fevening of April 6, despite them
OL,17,Faveraging at 18C for the afternoon,
OL,18,FCNN reported.
