OL,6,FAnother made $20,000 (around #14,800)
OL,7,Ffor predicting a similar spike on
OL,8,FApril 15.
OL,10,FCybercrime experts are now looking
OL,11,Finto what happened following a police
OL,12,Fcomplaint from Meteo-France.
